com.example.meditrackr.models.record

Class Record

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.meditrackr.models.record.Record
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Record
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Record: Stores all information associated with a record object, including 0 to 10 images, a timestamp (date), a description, a title, a geolocation and a body location. Records have a PhotoList, an ImageSave (list of string photo names for storage), a BodyLocation and a Geolocation.
    See Also:
    PhotoList, BodyLocation, Geolocation, Serialized Form
